<i>noun</i>: 슬픔 [슬픔], 설움 [서ː룸], 서러움 [서ː러움], 비애 [비ː애] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>슬픔 [슬픔]</dt><br>
<dd>sadness; sorrow</dd><br>
<dd>마음이 아프거나 괴로운 느낌.</dd><br>
<dd>A feeling of being distressed or in pain.</dd><br>
<dt>설움 [서ː룸]</dt><br>
<dd>sorrow; sadness</dd><br>
<dd>억울하고 슬픈 느낌이나 마음.</dd><br>
<dd>A feeling of sadness or sorrow.</dd><br>
<dt>서러움 [서ː러움]</dt><br>
<dd>sorrow; sadness</dd><br>
<dd>억울하고 슬픈 느낌이나 마음.</dd><br>
<dd>A sad, depressed feeling or mind.</dd><br>
<dt>비애 [비ː애]</dt><br>
<dd>grief; sorrow</dd><br>
<dd>슬픔과 서러움.</dd><br>
<dd>A mixture of sadness and heartache.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>